svg.title: storyboard
svg.text: Susan hasn’t slept in days. She has three exams and an eight-page essay due this week.
She takes out her last pair of clean socks. She decides that she'll do her laundry later while studying.
That evening, she throws everything that’s in her hamper into the washing machine, then tosses in two Tide Pods.
She is confused by all of the controls she sees... but when she sees "quick wash", she happily selects it.
When she presses the start button, nothing happens. She presses it again, and again, and grows frustrated.
When she takes a step back to take a breath, the machine makes a click and starts spinning. Puzzled but content, she returns to her room to
30 minutes later her timer goes off, and she moves the load into the drying machine.
